For those having audio issues.

A simple solution is to use MKVmerge to drop the Russian audio and subtitle streams, and remux the file so it only has the English audio and subtitles.

Takes about 10-12 minutes.

To add to my last post.

DON'T OVERWRITE THE ORIGINAL FILE UNLESS YOU ARE DONE RE-SEEDING BACK !!!

If you overwrite, you will mess it up for sharing with others.  Write ANOTHER copy, then view that one.....again, unless you are done seeding.
